title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jan 6 2022

description:
Clay and Buck interview Julie Kelly, senior contributor to American Greatness and author of January 6: How Democrats Used the Capitol Protest to Launch a War on Terror Against the Political Right. Clay donates $10K to the legal defense fund for Jan. 6th political prisoners. Leftists revel in persecuting and punishing the unvaccinated. C&B go to the phones.
